        "description": "Experimental test conditions must match simulation boundary conditions within ±5% for flow rate and ±3% for rotational speed. Blood analogue fluid properties must be documented with uncertainty bounds."
      },
      "rationale": "Bench tests conducted using porcine blood at 37 °C with documented hematocrit 38±2%. Flow rate controlled to ±2.1% and rotational speed to ±0.8% of nominal. Temperature maintained at 37±0.5 °C throughout. Full test protocol documented in TR-COU2-EXP-2025."
