        "description": "Normalized hemolysis index error must be <15% at all five operating points. Velocity field comparison (PIV vs CFD) must achieve mean absolute error <10% of bulk velocity. Uncertainty intervals must overlap between simulation and experiment."
      },
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index normalized error ranged 3.2–11.8% across five operating points. PIV velocity MAE was 7.4% of bulk velocity. Simulation 95% confidence intervals overlapped experimental uncertainty bounds at all operating points. Comparison documented in VR-COU2-COMP-2025."
    },
