        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Equivalency of input parameters acceptance criteria — COU2",
        "description": "Simulation boundary conditions must be demonstrably equivalent to experimental conditions. A formal equivalency mapping table must document each input parameter, its experimental value, its simulation value, and the method of equivalence verification."
      },
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping table completed for 18 input parameters. Flow rate, rotational speed, fluid temperature, hematocrit, and geometric dimensions verified equivalent within stated uncertainty bounds. Discrepancies in inlet velocity profile shape characterized and propagated as UQ input uncertainty. Equivalency report EQ-COU2-2025 reviewed and approved."
